{"surface":"وَمِنَ","context":"وَمِنَ النَّاسِ","wrong":"and whoever","correct":"and from / and among","reason":"kasra on mīm under the و proclitic → preposition, not وَمَن"}
{"surface":"لَمْ","context":"لَمْ يَلِدْ","wrong":"why","correct":"did not","reason":"negation + jussive"}
