{"surface":"لِمَا","context":"مُصَدِّقًا لِّمَا بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ","wrong":"when","correct":"for / that which","reason":"لِ + relative مَا; لَمَّا \"when\" carries shadda on the mīm"}
