{"surface":"نِعْمَ","context":"نِعْمَ الثَّوَابُ","wrong":"yes","correct":"how excellent / what a good","reason":"kasra on nūn → verb of praise; نَعَمْ \"yes\" has fatḥa"}
{"surface":"أَنِّى","context":"أَنِّى أَنَا الْغَفُورُ","wrong":"how?","correct":"that I","reason":"kasra cluster on nūn → أَنَّ + ـِي; أَنَّى \"how/whence\" has fatḥa"}
