{"surface":"وَيَقْدِرُ","context":"يَبْسُطُ الرِّزْقَ لِمَن يَشَاءُ وَيَقْدِرُ","correct":"restricts / straitens","reason":"paired antonym with يَبْسُط → restricts, not merely \"ordains\""}
